edia:description type="plain">Kamala Harris, former Vice President and 2024 Presidential candidate, arrives during the National Action Network (NAN) Convention in New York on April 10, 2026.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-kamala-2-gk-b85cb9.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Mario Tama</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Kamala Harris Book Tour In Los Angeles</media:text><media:description type="plain">Harris spoke in Los Angeles in September for her book tour.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-kamala-gk-887b62.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Jill Connelly</media:credit><media:text type="plain">California Gov. Newsom Attends A &#34;Yes On Prop 50&#34; Volunteer Event In L.A.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Harris spoke at a &#34;Yes on Prop 50&#34; volunteer event at the Los Angeles Convention Center in November.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260410-Kamala-Harris-ew-1202p-a7a29c.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate><title>Kamala Harris wants the DNC to release its autopsy report of the 2024 campaign</title><updateDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 09:00:00 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Elizabeth Chuck</dc:creator><dc:creator>Matt Lavietes</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Thu, 07 May 2026 09:00:00 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Thomas Shaknovsky said in a deposition in November that he believed he was removing 70-year-old William Bryan’s spleen, not his liver.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/florida-surgeon-removed-wrong-organ-t