he is ‘forever traumatized’ by patient’s death</title><updateDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 09:00:00 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Wed, 06 May 2026 23:10:59 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>A federal judge has unsealed a purported suicide note possibly written by notorious sex offender Jeffrey Epstein weeks before his death. It appears to state, in part, “they investigated me for months - found nothing” and “time to say goodbye.” NBC News’ Laura Jarrett has the latest.</description><expires>2056-05-06T23:04:35.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">nn_lja_jeffreyepsteinpossiblesuicidenote_260506</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/nightly-news/video/jeffrey-epstein-possible-suicide-note-released-262877765633</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nn_lja_jeffreyepsteinpossiblesuicidenote_260506/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Jeffrey Epstein possible suicide note released</media:title><media:player url="https://www.nbcnews.com/nightly-news/video/jeffrey-epstein-possible-suicide-note-released-262877765633"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778108665437_nn_lja_jeffreyepsteinpossiblesuicidenote_260506_S3_1920x1080-ztma5m.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">A federal judge has unsealed a purported suicide note possibly written by notorious sex offender Jeffrey Epstein weeks before his death. It appears to state, in part, “they investigated me for months - found nothing” and “time to say goodbye.” NBC News’ Laura Jarrett has the latest.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778108665437_nn_lja_jeffreyepsteinpossiblesuicidenote_260506.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News